<template>
  <v-dialog
      v-model="getShow"
      max-width="1400"
      max-height="960"
    >
      <v-card>
        <!-- top zone -->
        <v-container class="ma-0 pa-0 d-flex justify-space-between align-center">
          <v-card-title class="text-h4 font-weight-bold ">Gallery</v-card-title>
          <v-btn
          icon
          @click="backOpenGallery"
          class="mr-0">
            <v-icon width="100">{{icons.closeWindow}}</v-icon>
          </v-btn>
        </v-container>
          
      </v-card>
    </v-dialog>
</template>

<script>
export default {
    name: 'ImageGallery',
    props: {
      showDialog: {
        type: Boolean,
        required: true,
      }
    },
    data() {
      return {
        icons:{
          closeWindow: 'mdi-window-close'
        }
      }
    },
    computed:{
      getShow(){
        let localShow = this.showDialog
        return localShow
      }
    },
    methods: {
      backOpenGallery(){
        this.$emit('backOpenGallery',false)
      }
    },
    
}
</script>

<style>

</style>
